text.tspan: Total confirmed COVID-19 deaths vs. cases, Feb 28, 2023
The number of confirmed cases is lower than the number of total cases. The main reason for this is limited testing. The
grey lines show the corresponding case fatality rates, CFR (the ratio between confirmed deaths and confirmed cases).
